Ranger Help for: arcticsurvival
================================

SYNTAX:      arcticsurvival
             arctic survival
USAGE:       Hyperborea and other extreme arctic terrain
SLOT COST:   14
BASE SP:     10
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill toggles arctic survival instincts on or off. When active,
the Ranger reads snow, wind, exposure, and shelter well enough to avoid
the punishing Hyperborean cold that normally forces travelers to rely on
warmth protection.

Use this before crossing Hyperborea's frozen roads, tunnels, icefields,
and wilderness. Toggle it again to relax those instincts.

SEE ALSO: desert survival, rest, guide, terrains
